				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It could, in theory, but there are a number of complications.<br /><br />1. Still don't know what register to read back for the write (A, X, Y?)<br />2. $4014 is written only once per frame. $2000 is often written several times per-frame with differing values. The last one before OAM DMA might not be the correct one. You might need a way to trigger the drawing at the end of vblank or some other time besides when $4014 is written, etc. etc.<br /><br />So... go ahead and write a more complicated script to try and solve the problem generically, if you like. I spent maybe 10 minutes on this script, trying to solve that harder problem would probably take hours, and it's simply not worth my time. (Super easy to just customize the simple script per-game, anyway. Would rather spend 1 minute altering the script 10 times, than all day 1 time.)</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

